    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What do you get when you mix FPS, Roguelike, Parkour, and... robots that want to destroy you? TowerUp!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>In the main mode, you’re a robot (yes, <i>another</i> robot... but this one has attitude and an endless supply of bad jokes). Your &quot;dream job&quot;? Escaping from a magic portal, navigating through rooms filled with traps and robots that only exist to mess with you. The cherry on top? Every time you die (and oh, you’ll die <i>a lot</i>), you earn money and upgrades. Because, let’s face it, dying should have <i>some</i> perks, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br><br><br>Game modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TowerUp</strong>: The main adventure where you fight robots, explore a procedurally generated complex filled with enemies, and try to take down the company that, surprise, created you. Easy peasy... or not.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duelo</strong>: Because nothing says &quot;friendship&quot; like challenging your buddy to a 1v1 and rubbing those kills in their face.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arena</strong>: Like Duelo, but now with teams of up to 5 robots, ready to see who can wreak the most havoc in a massive map.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135450/extras/c7fdfadfa8e155dfc9cf6e10b936fa92.avif?t=1744051577\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135450/extras_big/c7fdfadfa8e155dfc9cf6e10b936fa92.avif?t=1744051577 width=800 height=267 /></span><br><br><br>But believe me, TowerUp isn’t just about <i>how many times you’ll die</i>. It’s also about moving with style: parkour, insane jumps, and that sweet, sweet feeling of gliding over enemy robots while pulling off some cinematic shots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br><br>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer, Multiplayer, and modes that will test your patience and reflexes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A power-up system that makes the chaos <i>even more fun</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultra-dynamic movement – because walking in a straight line is for chumps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of robots... but you’re <i>the</i> robot with guns and a dream of destruction!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br><br>TowerUp: be the robot everyone wants to see blow the place up!</strong></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 俄语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
